txt.en: 'Well done! Though I don't know where you put all of that food. It's almost like you have...more than one stomach, or something.\n\n'It's very strange, if you ask me...But yes, well done! Not many patrons make it as far as the final station. I imagine you'll need to walk a bit, now...or perhaps curl up in the gutter somewhere.'
